{"tid":1507183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人受軟定受硬？錯了，我地支持魚蛋論！","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T00:28:16.000Z","uid":70769,"like":91,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b2174e8233c671e38ee1cafaec69b46e63c6ba8a","tid":1507183,"uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"港共而為打壓可以令我地滅聲？<br />\n港共而為派糖可以令我地滅聲？<br />\n港共打算軟硬兼施可以令我地滅聲？<br />\n<br />\n錯哂！我地只會接受魚蛋論。<br />\n我少左一粒魚蛋？我都要你少一粒魚蛋！<br />\n你告犯法市民坐監，我地都要你問責落台，犯法警員坐監，鄉黑受應有懲罰！<br />\n<br />\n魚蛋論背後核心係絕對公平！一係一齊行生路，一係一齊攬炒。帶全香港750萬人大家一齊行生路唔係我地話到事，但係帶750萬人一齊攬炒共享大灣區就係我地能力做到！<br />\n<br />\n請大家出來，一齊大大力錫政府春袋！"},{"pid":"ce54598a79d01071f1ced58b20906c145f235060","tid":1507183,"uid":36378,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"我無你都唔可以有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c342d83da6712aedf77c57aa859e2424b1dd62","tid":1507183,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aeNRkyU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aeNRkyU</a>"},{"pid":"a64686c6300f35013dfa64446520e915b9a512be","tid":1507183,"uid":137588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:07:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n[整合] 反送中運動白色恐怖時間表<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507141</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"685268c757ed67fafaac8705b602d220e73c0767","tid":1507183,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"316213d162878f6c01560093dad0c0c58b4dbe76","tid":1507183,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:10:49.0